		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Maybe a better description (or even a screenshot) of the glitch would help. And sometimes it's hard to tell where a bug is... you may think it's in a piece of code you posted, but it may very well be caused by something completely different, and that piece might just be what makes the bug evident, not what causes it.

		

