		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">tokumaru wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">you may think it's in a piece of code you posted, but it may very well be caused by something completely different, and that piece might just be what makes the bug evident, not what causes it.</div>
<br />
<br />Completely true. A lot of the time, the problem is quite simple, like a typo. But the typo could be anywhere. Use the process of elimination to determine where your bug has to be. By testing code under different circumstances, you can usually get to the bottom of it fairly quickly.

		

